Actions.Text: AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO GOVERNMENTAL EMPLOYEES

Title: Authorizes Stephen Watkins to receive certain service credit under section 384-d of the retirement and social security law
Summary: Authorizes Stephen Watkins to receive certain service credit under section 384-d of the retirement and social security law.
